snippet.title: Storebound | Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Revealing Storebound! Set in a nightmarish furniture store, you must find the exit and escape. But when the lights go out, everything changes. Scavenge for tools and supplies, work together with your friends, or you’ll become part of the store forever.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3417410/Storebound/
Follow on TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@storebound 
Follow on Instagram: https://www.tiktok.com/@storebound
